TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup target table TRECONCILIATION to check the existance of source record.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: Lkp_TRECONCILIATION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Route input records to two outputs - New and Changed, based on New and Changed flags. When New Flag =1then record is inserted into the target TRBI table "GDXDM.TRECONCILIATION". When Changed Flag= 1then record is updated into the target TRBI table "GDXDM.TRECONCILIATION".
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: Rtr_New_Change_flag

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Extract records for timestamp>'$$LOAD_LAST_TS'. Initial value of parameter $$LOAD_LAST_TS is '01/01/1111 00:00:00' and is get updated with UPDT_TS value. The join to RCNH_RECN_HDR is to get the create user id for the first time this record exists. The target USR_ID will never be updated after the initial insert to the TRBI target, but because the user id on the RCNT_RECN_HDR can change moments after the initial insert to the value 'INFA', users wanted to capture that initial user which meant looking to the insert record on the RCNH table.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_TRECONCILIATION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: VRAP.RCNT_RECN_HDR.LAST_UPDT_TS>TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS' ) AND VRAP.RCNH_RECN_HDR .HIST_INSRT_REAS_CD ='I' --the join to RCNH_RECN_HDR is to get the create user id for the first time this record exists. The target USR_ID will never be updated after the initial insert to the TRBI target, but because the user id on the RCNT_RECN_HDR can change moments after the initial insert to 'INFA', users wanted to capture that initial user which meant looking to the RCNH table.

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Check if source row exist in target table a) if present then compare the column values of source and target. If there is a difference then set CHANGE_FLAG = 1 to denote it as changed record else CHANGE_FLAG = 0 b) If not present then set NEW_FLAG=1 to denote as new record.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: Exp_Detect_changes

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(Tgt_RCNCLN_ID) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_CORP_OWNR_ID) AND (Tgt_RCNCLN_CRTE_DT!=var_RCNCLN_CRTE_DT or Tgt_RCNCLN_CRTE_USR_ID!=var_RCNCLN_CRTE_USR_ID or Tgt_RCNCLN_STUS_CD!=Src_RCNCLN_STUS_CD or LTRIM(RTRIM(Tgt_RCNCLN_ID_TX))!=LTRIM(RTRIM(Src_RCNCLN_ID_TX)) or Tgt_RCNCLN_VNDR_ID!=Src_RCNCLN_VNDR_ID or Tgt_RCNCLN_BUS_ID!=Src_RCNCLN_BUS_ID or LTRIM(RTRIM(Tgt_RCNCLN_INV_PRD_ID))!=LTRIM(RTRIM(var_RCNCLN_INV_PRD_ID))), 1, 0 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: Change_Flag
